{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_TossArm}}
'''A_TossArm'''

(no parameters)

Spawns an {{Class|InquisitorArm}} at the calling actor's position, 24 units up from the base of the calling actor's feet. The arm's angle is set randomly to between 0° and 180° from the calling actor's angle, at one-eighth of the base's Speed property. It is also given a random vertical velocity of up to 4.0. 

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|Inquisitor}} and derived classes.

